## Limitations

The primary limitation of this report is the reliance on available online sources, which may not encompass the full spectrum of academic discourse on the topic. Additionally, the interpretation of sex as a social construct is subject to ongoing debate and may vary across different cultural and academic contexts. The report does not delve into the biological sciences' perspective in depth, which could provide a more comprehensive understanding of the biological aspects of sex.

